	(**The type of arrays with capabilities.
	   An [('a, [`Read | `Write])] array behaves as a regular ['a array],
	   while a [('a, [`Read]) array] only has read-only capabilities
	   and a [('a, [`Write]) array] only has write-only capabilities.*)

